const pages = dv.pages("#BloodTest").where(b=>b.Triglyceride && b.HDL).sort(b => b.Date);

const data = pages.map(b=>b["Triglyceride"]/b["HDL"]);
 

const chartData = {
    type: 'line',
    data: {        
		labels: labels.values,
        datasets: [{
            label: 'Triglycerides-to-HDL Ratio',
